00:55:55.639 --> 00:55:58.648
lightclient: And if we can't even, you know, solve this one.

364
00:55:59.389 --> 00:56:02.070
lightclient: Like, I worry about our ability to continue

365
00:56:02.300 --> 00:56:06.320
